1. *Doneli* su mi poklon za rođendan. (They brought me a gift for my birthday.)
2. Da li si *donela* novac koji si pozajmila? (Did you bring back the money you borrowed?)
3. Oni su *donosili* hranu za napuštene pse. (They used to bring food for the stray dogs.)
4. Ja sam im *donio* knjigu koju su tražili. (I brought them the book they asked for.)
5. Vi ste *doneli* odluku bez konsultovanja sa mnom. (You made the decision without consulting me.)
6. Kada ste *donosili* odluke, niste razmišljali o posledicama. (When you were making decisions, you didn't think about the consequences.)
7. *Donosite* veliku odgovornost na svojim ramenima. (You carry a great responsibility on your shoulders.)
8. Ona je *donela* kafu i čaj za sve goste. (She brought coffee and tea for all the guests.)
9. Mi smo *doneli* odluku da napustimo grad. (We made the decision to leave the city.)
10. Kada *doneseš* odluku, javi mi. (When you make a decision, let me know.)